Business Brief -- Amtech Corp.:
   Pact Reached on Installing
   Toll System in Hong Kong
Amtech said the pilot program contract is valued at
$375,000 to $400,000.
   Separately, Amtech said its board approved a 3-for-2 stock
split to be distributed Feb. 13 to shares of record Jan. 24.
The split will increase shares outstanding to 10.1 million
from about 6.8 million.